  "body": "### User Story\n\nAs a user looking for new contacts, I want the option to pay tribute to people I am interested in speaking with.\n\n### Description\n\n*Type*: Feature\n\n*Summary*: New system message required.\n\nSee [row 3 Figma designs](https://www.figma.com/file/aS1ct66VQ6V0cio7vSqS8UoG/Chat?node-id=1319%3A13403)\n\ncc @errorists for further chat specs.\n\n#### Expected behavior\nWhen I try to chat with a user who has TtT set, I receive the below message with option to pay user. When I choose `Pay N SNT`, a wallet transaction with the correct amount is triggered. \n\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15470435/50904317-49bad200-1420-11e9-8b4d-82fd77033948.png\" width=250/>\n\n*note* the personalised message is optional and depends on whether user has set one.\n\nThis issue & #7235 should use the same `learn more` screen.",
